Motormaster emerges from the Dark Avian, "I just got a message from
Speedbreaker," he finishes looking at Speedbreaker. "Well, I'm sure a
shuttle just passed that way and set down" he said. Motormaster looks to
Dead End, "Do your thing" he told him, implying to the radar.
